<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='239000' id='t-239000'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:15
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='244000' id='t-244000'>These days an iPod Classic can hold 40,000 songs,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='247000' id='t-247000'>which is to say eight billion dollars-worth</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='250000' id='t-250000'>of stolen media.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='252000' id='t-252000'>(Applause)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='254000' id='t-254000'>Or about 75,000 jobs.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:27
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='256000' id='t-256000'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
