 4:29
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='258000' id='t-258000'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:34
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='263000' id='t-263000'>Now you might find copyright math strange,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='266000' id='t-266000'>but that's because it's a field</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='268000' id='t-268000'>that's best left to experts.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='270000' id='t-270000'>So that's it for now.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='272000' id='t-272000'>I hope you'll join me next time</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='274000' id='t-274000'>when I will be making an equally scientific and fact-based inquiry</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='277000' id='t-277000'>into the cost of alien music piracy to he American economy.</span>
</span>
</p>
